data.title: Statik GK in English
data.meta_description: Statik GK in English - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document summarizes Indian folk dances and artists from different states of India. Some key dances mentioned from Andhra Pradesh include Kummi, Siddhi Madhuri, Ghanta Mardala, Butta Bommalu, Bhamakalpam, Dappu, Tappeta Gullu, Lambadi, Dhimsa, Kolattam, Veeranatyam, Gobbi, Dandaria, Bonalu. From Assam, dances mentioned include Bichhua, Natpuja, Maharas, Khel Gopal, Bihu, Ankiya Nat, Kaligopal, Naga Nirtya Bagurumba, Konai, Jhumur. It
